<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0">
<title>Lógica Matemática · Clase 8 · UdeC</title>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#06090f; --card:rgba(255,255,255,.05); --border:rgba(255,255,255,.1); --border2:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  --text:#f1f0f8; --muted:#9090b0;
  --L1:#6ee7b7; --L1bg:rgba(52,211,153,.13); --L1b:rgba(52,211,153,.3);
  --L2:#93c5fd; --L2bg:rgba(59,130,246,.13); --L2b:rgba(59,130,246,.3);
  --L3:#c4b5fd; --L3bg:rgba(139,92,246,.13); --L3b:rgba(139,92,246,.3);
  --L4:#fca5a5; --L4bg:rgba(239,68,68,.13);  --L4b:rgba(239,68,68,.3);
  --Lo:#fcd34d; --Lobg:rgba(245,158,11,.13); --Lob:rgba(245,158,11,.3);
  --Co:#fb7185; --Cobg:rgba(244,63,94,.13); --Cob:rgba(244,63,94,.3);
  --Cl:#a78bfa; --Clbg:rgba(139,92,246,.13);
  --serif:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;
  --sans:-apple-system,'Segoe UI',sans-serif; --mono:'Courier New',monospace;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
body{
  font-family:var(--sans);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;
  background-color:var(--bg);
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 60% at 10% 0%,rgba(139,92,246,.2) 0%,transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 90% 100%,rgba(245,158,11,.12) 0%,transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 50% 50%,rgba(59,130,246,.08) 0%,transparent 60%);
  background-attachment:fixed;padding-bottom:60px;
}
body::before{
  content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;
  background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='700' height='500' viewBox='0 0 700 500' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M50 250 Q175 100 350 250 Q525 400 650 250' fill='none' stroke='rgba(139,92,246,0.05)' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Cpath d='M0 300 Q350 50 700 300' fill='none' stroke='rgba(245,158,11,0.04)' stroke-width='1.5'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='100' cy='80' r='2' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.06)'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='400' cy='60' r='1.5' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.05)'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='620' cy='100' r='2' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.04)'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='250' cy='450' r='1.5' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.05)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size:700px 500px;
}
/* HEADER */
.hdr{position:relative;z-index:2;background:rgba(6,9,15,.85);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);padding:18px 16px 0;overflow:hidden;}
.hdr::after{content:'p→q';position:absolute;right:-8px;top:-16px;font-size:110px;font-family:var(--mono);font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(167,139,250,.18),transparent);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;pointer-events:none;}
.hdr-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;background:var(--L3bg);border:1px solid var(--L3b);color:var(--L3);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:99px;font-size:.6rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px;}
.hdr h1{font-family:var(--serif);color:#fff;font-size:1.28rem;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:2px;position:relative;}
.hdr h1 em{color:var(--Lo);font-style:normal;}
.hdr p{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px;}
.tabs{display:flex;overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none;gap:0;}
.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
.tab{flex-shrink:0;padding:8px 11px 7px;font-size:.6rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;transition:all .2s;user-select:none;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;white-space:nowrap;}
.tab .ti{display:block;font-size:1rem;text-align:center;margin-bottom:2px;}
.tab.on{color:#fff;}
.tab[data-m="0"].on{border-bottom-color:#f43f5e;color:#fb7185;}
.tab[data-m="1"].on{border-bottom-color:var(--L1);color:var(--L1);}
.tab[data-m="2"].on{border-bottom-color:var(--L2);color:var(--L2);}
.tab[data-m="3"].on{border-bottom-color:var(--L3);color:var(--L3);}
.tab[data-m="4"].on{border-bottom-color:var(--Co);color:var(--Co);}
.tab[data-m="5"].on{border-bottom-color:var(--Lo);color:var(--Lo);}
.tab[data-m="6"].on{border-bottom-color:var(--Cl);color:var(--Cl);}
/* LAYOUT */
.wrap{max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 14px 8px;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.mod{display:none;}.mod.on{display:block;}
/* SESSION BADGES */
.srow{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:10px;}
.sb{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:99px;font-size:.58rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;}
.sb-clase{background:rgba(52,211,153,.12);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.3);color:var(--L1);}
.sb-casa{background:rgba(245,158,11,.12);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.3);color:var(--Lo);}
.sb-coop{background:rgba(244,63,94,.12);border:1px solid rgba(244,63,94,.3);color:var(--Co);}
/* CARDS */
.card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:12px;box-shadow:0 6px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.3),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.07);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);}
.ct{font-size:.6rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.section-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;}
/* CONTEXT BOX */
.ctx{border-radius:11px;padding:12px 14px;margin:10px 0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.ctx-label{font-size:.58rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:5px;}
.ctx-body{font-size:.82rem;line-height:1.7;}
.ctx-body code{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.8rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;}
/* PROPOSITION CARDS */
.prop-cards{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;margin:10px 0;}
.prop-card{border-radius:9px;padding:11px 13px;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;user-select:none;}
.prop-card:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.prop-card .pc-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:6px;}
.prop-card .pc-tag{display:none;font-size:.73rem;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;margin-top:6px;}
.prop-card.revealed .pc-tag{display:block;}
/* TRUTH TABLE */
.tt{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.82rem;font-family:var(--mono);margin:8px 0;}
.tt th{padding:7px 10px;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;text-align:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:var(--muted);}
.tt td{padding:8px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;}
.tt tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);}
.tv{font-weight:700;color:var(--L1);}
.tf{font-weight:700;color:var(--L4);}
/* FORMULA DISPLAY */
.formula-big{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;text-align:center;padding:14px;border-radius:10px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid;}
/* INTERACTIVE CONNECTOR */
.conn-demo{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin:10px 0;}
.conn-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:9px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.conn-sym{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;min-width:30px;text-align:center;}
.conn-ex{font-size:.8rem;flex:1;line-height:1.5;}
.conn-result{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.85rem;font-weight:700;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:6px;}
/* CONDITIONAL */
.cond-table{width:100%;margin:8px 0;}
.cond-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto auto auto auto;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px;align-items:center;}
.cond-cell{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.82rem;text-align:center;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:7px;border:1px solid var(--border2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);}
.cond-cell.highlight{border-color:var(--L4);background:var(--L4bg);color:var(--L4);font-weight:700;}
.cond-cell.hdr{font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);border:none;background:transparent;}
/* DEMORGAN CONNECTION */
.demorgan-card{border-radius:10px;padding:13px;border:1.5px solid;margin:8px 0;}
.dm-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:.83rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:6px;}
.dm-symbol{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;min-width:28px;text-align:center;}
/* COOPERATIVE */
.coop-block{border-radius:13px;border:2px solid var(--Cob);background:rgba(244,63,94,.05);padding:14px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.coop-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.coop-icon{font-size:1.4rem;}
.coop-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;color:var(--Co);}
.coop-timer{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:99px;background:var(--Cobg);border:1px solid var(--Cob);color:var(--Co);}
.step-coop{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:9px;font-size:.82rem;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:8px;}
.sc-n{min-width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;background:var(--Cobg);color:var(--Co);border:1px solid var(--Cob);}
.role-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--border2);font-size:.79rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:5px;}
.role-tag{font-size:.57rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:99px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}
/* INTERDEPENDENCE BADGE */
.inter-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:4px 11px;border-radius:99px;font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;border:1px solid;margin-bottom:8px;}
/* ARGUMENT CARDS */
.arg-card{border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;margin-bottom:8px;transition:all .18s;}
.arg-card:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.arg-card .arg-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:.83rem;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:6px;}
.arg-card .arg-ans{display:none;font-size:.77rem;line-height:1.55;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:8px;margin-top:6px;animation:fadeIn .25s ease;}
.arg-card.open .arg-ans{display:block;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(4px);}to{opacity:1;transform:none;}}
/* QUIZ */
.quiz-q{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:13px;margin-bottom:10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);}
.quiz-q-num{font-size:.6rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:5px;}
.quiz-q-text{font-size:.86rem;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:10px;}
.quiz-q-text .mono{font-family:var(--mono);background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;font-size:.82rem;}
.quiz-opts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;}
.quiz-opt{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;padding:8px 11px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1.5px solid var(--border);font-size:.81rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;user-select:none;line-height:1.4;}
.quiz-opt:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.quiz-opt input{margin-top:2px;flex-shrink:0;accent-color:var(--Lo);}
.quiz-opt.sel{background:var(--Lobg);border-color:var(--Lob);}
.quiz-opt.ok{background:var(--L1bg)!important;border-color:var(--L1b)!important;color:var(--L1);}
.quiz-opt.ko{background:var(--L4bg)!important;border-color:var(--L4b)!important;color:var(--L4);}
.quiz-submit{width:100%;padding:13px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(245,158,11,.9),rgba(180,83,9,.9));color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:11px;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;margin-top:14px;font-family:var(--sans);transition:all .15s;}
.quiz-submit:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.quiz-submit:disabled{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);cursor:not-allowed;color:var(--muted);}
.score-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(139,92,246,.18),rgba(245,158,11,.1));border:1px solid rgba(167,139,250,.4);border-radius:14px;padding:20px;margin-top:14px;text-align:center;display:none;animation:fadeIn .4s ease;}
.score-num{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--Lo);display:block;line-height:1;}
.score-bar{height:8px;border-radius:99px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);margin:12px 0;overflow:hidden;}
.score-fill{height:100%;border-radius:99px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--L1),var(--Lo));transition:width 1s ease;}
.score-msg{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:.88rem;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.6;}
.q-fb{font-size:.77rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:8px;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:8px;display:none;}
.q-fb.ok{background:var(--L1bg);border:1px solid var(--L1b);color:var(--L1);}
.q-fb.ko{background:var(--L4bg);border:1px solid var(--L4b);color:var(--L4);}
.quiz-saved-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:99px;font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;background:rgba(52,211,153,.1);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.25);color:var(--L1);margin-bottom:8px;}
/* HOMEWORK */
.hw-section{border-radius:12px;padding:13px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1.5px solid;}
.hw-section-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:5px;}
.hw-section-sub{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.5;}
.hw-ex{border-radius:8px;padding:10px 12px;margin-bottom:7px;border:1px solid var(--border2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:all .15s;}
.hw-ex:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.hw-ex-q{font-size:.82rem;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:5px;}
.hw-ex-q .mono{font-family:var(--mono);background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;font-size:.78rem;}
.hw-ex-opts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;margin:6px 0;}
.hw-ex-opt{display:flex;gap:7px;font-size:.78rem;padding:5px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border2);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:all .12s;}
.hw-ex-opt:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.hw-ex-opt.hw-sel{background:var(--Lobg);border-color:var(--Lob);}
.hw-ex-opt.hw-ok{background:var(--L1bg);border-color:var(--L1b);color:var(--L1);}
.hw-ex-opt.hw-ko{background:var(--L4bg);border-color:var(--L4b);color:var(--L4);}
.hw-ex-reveal{display:none;font-size:.76rem;padding:7px 9px;border-radius:7px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.55;animation:fadeIn .25s ease;}
.hw-ex.open .hw-ex-reveal{display:block;}
.hw-reveal-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;margin-top:6px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:99px;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;}
.hw-progress{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;margin-top:4px;}
/* STUDY PLAN */
.study-day{border-radius:10px;padding:11px 13px;margin-bottom:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);}
.study-day-title{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.study-day-desc{font-size:.8rem;line-height:1.55;color:var(--muted);}
/* MISC */
.hint{font-size:.74rem;color:var(--muted);background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-left:3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:7px 9px;border-radius:0 9px 9px 0;margin:7px 0;line-height:1.5;}
.alert{padding:10px 12px;border-radius:9px;font-size:.78rem;line-height:1.6;margin:8px 0;}
.al-L1{background:var(--L1bg);border:1px solid var(--L1b);color:var(--L1);}
.al-Lo{background:var(--Lobg);border:1px solid var(--Lob);color:var(--Lo);}
.al-L3{background:var(--L3bg);border:1px solid var(--L3b);color:var(--L3);}
.al-Co{background:var(--Cobg);border:1px solid var(--Cob);color:var(--Co);}
.nav{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px;}
.btn{padding:10px 16px;border:none;border-radius:9px;font-size:.83rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;font-family:var(--sans);}
.btn:active{transform:scale(.97);}
.btn-next{flex:2;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(245,158,11,.8),rgba(180,83,9,.8));}
.btn-back{flex:1;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);}
hr.div{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border2);margin:12px 0;}
.two-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin:8px 0;}
@media(max-width:380px){.two-col{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
/* FOOTER */
.page-footer{margin-top:24px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:20px 16px 32px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.page-footer::before{content:'p→q  ¬p  p∧q  p∨q';font-family:var(--mono);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--L1),var(--L2),var(--L3),var(--Lo));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;opacity:.07;position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;}
.footer-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;}
/* TOAST */
#toast{position:fixed;bottom:20px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(80px);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--Lo),rgba(180,83,9,.9));color:#fff;padding:8px 20px;border-radius:99px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;z-index:9999;pointer-events:none;transition:transform .3s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);white-space:nowrap;}
#toast.show{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hdr">
  <div class="hdr-badge">Clase 8 · Miller §3 · Matemáticas I · 2026</div>
  <h1>Lógica <em>Proposicional</em></h1>
  <p>Psicología · UdeC Facatativá — El lenguaje de la argumentación científica</p>
  <div class="tabs">
    <div class="tab on" data-m="0" onclick="sw(0)"><span class="ti">🎬</span>Gancho</div>
    <div class="tab" data-m="1" onclick="sw(1)"><span class="ti">📝</span>Proposiciones</div>
    <div class="tab" data-m="2" onclick="sw(2)"><span class="ti">🔗</span>Conectivos</div>
    <div class="tab" data-m="3" onclick="sw(3)"><span class="ti">➡️</span>Condicional</div>
    <div class="tab" data-m="4" onclick="sw(4)"><span class="ti">👥</span>Cooperativo</div>
    <div class="tab" data-m="5" onclick="sw(5)"><span class="ti">📊</span>Quiz</div>
    <div class="tab" data-m="6" onclick="sw(6)"><span class="ti">🏠</span>Para Casa</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

<!-- ═══════ M0 GANCHO ═══════ -->
<div class="mod on" id="m0">
  <div class="srow"><span class="sb sb-clase">🎬 Abrir ANTES de la clase — gancho individual</span></div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ct">Antes de que el profesor empiece</div>
    <p class="section-title">¿Cuáles de estas frases pueden ser verdaderas o falsas?</p>
    <p style="font-size:.84rem;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:12px;">Sin haber visto nada sobre lógica todavía: toca cada frase e intenta clasificarla. ¿Tiene valor de verdad (puede ser V o F)? ¿O no tiene sentido preguntarse si es verdadera?</p>
